<div style="font-family: Courier; font-weight: bold;">
<p>执行<em>程序-[Format-Debug-R]</em>-<em>深度模因过滤</em>————</p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="border: 1px solid black; display: inline-block; width: 80%">
<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:100%;"><img src="https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-cn-1856/meme.png" style="width:100%;" alt="meme.png" class="image" />
